calculateChiSquaredStat

calculateChiSquaredStat.Rd

calculateChiSquaredStat Given a pair of C_alpha and C_beta chemical shifts, this function will return a list of caculated chisquare statistics basing on the combination of amino acid typings and secondary structures.

calculateChiSquaredStat(cacbPair)

Arguments

x

A pair of carbon chemical shifts (Ca, Cb)

Value

A list of chisquare statisitcs basing the combination of amino acid typings and secondary structures.

Examples

calculateChiSquaredStat(c(54,45))
